      "span_text": "Exposure to niclosamide alone provoked up-regulation of several features associated with response to xenobiotics including cytochrome p450s, heat shock proteins, multidrug resistant transporters and glutathione-S-transferases, confirming many of the observations made by Zhang et al  in a microarray study of B. glabrata exposed to sublethal doses of niclosamide.",
